{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"58331-mu-ku-ru-kya-ne-ga-to-kya-ne","title":"MUKURU CYANE! GATO CYANE!","description":"Shanu ni munini kuburyo Ami atamuterura. Ariko muto kuburyo atajya ku ishuri wenyine. Uri muto cyane ku buryo utasoma iyi nkuru wenyine? Uri mukuru kuburyo umuntu yagusomera iyi nkuru? Fungura maze urebe","language":"Kinyarwanda","langCode":"rw","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Fred HIRWA"],"illustrators":["Lavanya Karthik"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Right To Play","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/58331-mu-ku-ru-kya-ne-ga-to-kya-ne"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size3/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size6/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42853/size6/70fd0452aa6c927e53d76aa9fb3f4ffc.jpg","text":"Ami ati\"Nabasha kuguterura, Shanu\".","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42854/size6/fc8e07ddde1f569112ef4235e88c71fd.jpg","text":"Abu ati\"Ntabwo wajya ku ishuri wenyine, Shanu\".","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42855/size6/a26479a6b4ec64005cc22f1749c54a41.jpg","text":"Dadu ati\" Ntabwo waryama ku buriri bw'uruhinja, Shanu\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42856/size6/0a0aa02709c207420750b383dd405ace.jpg","text":"Dadi ati\" Ntabwo wajyana umwana muri parike\".","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/